    <p class="text-ink/70 mb-6">thaiholidaybudget.com uses only <strong>strictly-necessary local storage</strong> to make the estimator work — there are no advertising, analytics, or tracking cookies to manage. Below is exactly what is stored on your device, and you can clear it at any time.</p>

